item.title: Jooklo Duo, Mik Quantius
item.description: Jooklo Duo [chakric, mental no-jazz / Italy] Was about time to bring the Jooklo experience to our little fair city. Roaming the improv and weird music underground already since the mid-00’s, David Vanzan and Virginia Genta (also known through projects such as Golden Jooklo Age, Jooklo Quartet, Jooklo Stellar Tribe, Neokarma Jooklo Trio, New Jooklo Age etc.) will now play their first Leipzig show.
